    "presented Sageflow in [176] to handle slow devices and malicious attacks.",
    "Finally, Agarwal et al.",
    "extended differential privacy using the Skellam mechanism in [177].Additionally, many other cryptographic methods are widely used to preserve privacy in FL.",
    "Chang et al. [178] revisited many technologies in FL and propose 2DMCFE, a functional encryption method to protect privacy under semi-honest security setting.",
    "Furthermore, Hijazi et al. [179] also investigated the use of Fully Homomorphic Encryption (FHE) in FL."
